{"tid":447756,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"雪國","createTime":"2017-10-25T14:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T02:15:07.000Z","uid":73617,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb7c0aacc6285e2676bf1de115a370ff14ffd1c","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"「我叫T，26歲來自南邊沒有雪的小島，所以我喜歡雪。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七月嗰時因為有幾隊band一直好想睇，就決定去歐洲順面行下山。<br />\n路線都係就住d show黎plan，點知砌下砌下又幾順路。<br />\n<br />\n一開始係為左睇Arcade Fire先去意大利<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFmHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFmHN.jpg&h=39d19d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去南德Bavaria時順路去左Slovenia同Austria<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTHBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTHBs.jpg&h=edd9e4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入瑞士山區前返意大利熱身<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFxY6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFxY6.jpg&h=3c580bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTXwI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTXwI.jpg&h=badcaf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係Zermatt爬山都用左十幾日<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/z90Wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fz90Wf.jpg&h=410bc2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/z9mH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fz9mH8.jpg&h=3e34a375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTJdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTJdf.jpg&h=2c9cf0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用歐洲最高峰Mont Blanc埋尾<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTz6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTz6M.jpg&h=bcd76568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zF7cu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzF7cu.jpg&h=4fe4d883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行夠皮去巴黎睇Bon Iver<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFbyt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFbyt.jpg&h=e59d5dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTv6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTv6T.jpg&h=c51fafe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後返London追兩場The National<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFfeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFfeG.jpg&h=adc0187f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相係用iphone6同埋借返黎既sony a7影，但其實我未用過相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然亦都唔識執相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計埋帳篷睡袋行山boots同埋d gear、相機腳架立立雜雜約25kg<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/z430f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fz430f.jpg&h=59aad8b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nItinerary：Italy-Slovenia-Austria-Germany-Italy-Switzerland-France<br />\n<br />\nJul14-15 London<br />\nJul16-18 Milano<br />\nJul19-23 Roma<br />\nJul24-27 Firenze<br />\nJul28-29 Venezia<br />\n<br />\nJul29              Ljubljana<br />\nJul30-Aug02 Triglav National Park<br />\nAug03            Lienz<br />\nAug04-06      Hohe Tauern National Park<br />\nAug07-08      Salzburg<br />\nAug09            K&ouml;nigssee<br />\nAug10-13      Garmisch-Partenkirchen<br />\nAug14-15      F&uuml;ssen<br />\nAug16-20      M&uuml;nchen<br />\n<br />\nAug21-22 Gran Paradiso National Park<br />\nAug23-26 Milan<br />\nAug27-28 Luzern<br />\nAug29       Interlaken<br />\nAug30      Grindelwald<br />\nAug31      transfer to Visp<br />\n<br />\nSep01-13  Zermatt<br />\nSep14        transfer to Chamonix<br />\nSep15-21  Chamonix    <br />\nSep22        transfer to Paris<br />\nSep23-25  Paris<br />\nSep26-30  London<br />\n<br />\n因為我係歐洲流浪過一段時間，呢邊D野一早冷感晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使今次d地方未去過，好多所謂必去景點已經冇特別意慾想去，好多時露下營煮下飯又一日，所以一般歐遊事項會比較少，你當係行山post睇會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請睇#1-3前言。"},{"pid":"135ba43eb0923b3832a4c6ef8f62941a9554b70a","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"首先簡單介紹下今次行過既山先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMountaineering黎講，呢堆山唔難。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你用香港個套「行山」concept黎比既話，係會出事的。<br />\n蚺蛇尖狗牙嶺嗰d叫五星? 搞笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有千祈唔好以為山越高就越難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次唔係我第一次上雪山，事前亦有好多準備功夫，有咩問題我盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過，呢到始終只係一篇遊記，我將山上既事寫得顯淺易明係為左大家追故過癮d，唔建議用黎做任何技術參考。<br />\n<br />\n攀爬路線、red tape嗰d再逐個山詳細講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇用過任何lift / cable car上山，隨左Grossglockner衰天氣全部solo登頂。<br />\n<br />\n1. Triglav, Slovenia 2864m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFQWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFQWz.jpg&h=39e02fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. Grossglockner, Austria 3798m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTTjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTTjt.jpg&h=e3a7ac3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. Zugspitze, Germany 2962m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zT32p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzT32p.jpg&h=9d5c5ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. Gran Paradiso, Italy 4061m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTC4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTC4z.jpg&h=89cfbe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. Breithorn, Switzerland 4164m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTqpP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTqpP.jpg&h=0e01c0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Castor, Switzerland 4228m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTAPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTAPb.jpg&h=23eb9473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. Pullox, Switzerland 4092m<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zTWh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzTWh6.jpg&h=4ddefa2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. Mont Blanc, France 4810m, Highest peak of Europe*<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zT9B3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzT9B3.jpg&h=ddcfc8b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係瑞士仲去左Dufourspitze，不過攻頂前一晚飲完山水肚all爬都未爬就要落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*Russia同Geogria都分別有更高既山峰，但係因為Caucasus(高加索地區)既地理爭議性，有D人會當佢係亞洲多過歐洲。<br />\n<br />\n所以歐洲最高點既定義亦有Elbrus (5642m) 同 Mont Blanc (4810m)兩派。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外唔好以為行山唔點洗錢，我洗得最多就係山上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行「大山」兩日一夜或以上係好普遍，就算你唔介意係嚴苛既condition下露營，部份山頭因為environment law係嚴禁任何露宿行為，所以通常過夜都係喺山上既refuge / base camp。<br />\n<br />\n一般under各國山協既hut bunk bed for member 15~20eur/ night，但如果係出名或者私營既山屋可以去到60eur~/ night，half broad一般再加三十歐左右。<br />\n<br />\n呢d山屋往往亦係唯一既補給點，因為位置上既inaccessibility，食物同水唔係人力就係直升機運上去所以係好貴。<br />\n<br />\n你可以自備食物，不過長途線好難帶足咁多日糧水 (太重)，而且難保會有需要熱餐既時候。萬一有咩頭暈身慶，就算係放棄都需要食野先有體力落山，有時天氣突變焗住困多係山一兩日又唔定。<br />\n<br />\n所以我平時個budget都渣得幾緊下，就係驚係山上有咩事要用錢。"},{"pid":"0ccf87dfc4e6028ca49f2ba926252e9cfc5949eb","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為一定會有人問所以我直接寫埋喇。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n●用左幾錢：HKD$20,000-<br />\n<br />\n每個人用錢既考慮唔同，直接比較冇意思，簡單d講我得你未必得，我唔得既你又可能得。<br />\n<br />\n我本身有Couchsurfing開，今次好好彩多人host，同埋我有tent，campsite一般仲平過hostel，有時我直頭搵個公園／草地過夜就算 (EU好多城市都有campground，歐洲人好興campervan的)。食野自己煮+乾糧，同埋我多數係Hitchhike又慳唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n●我係寫遊記唔係寫攻略，唔好問我點慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我洗得少唔係因為我可以廿蚊食到米芝蓮三星，只係因為我真係食返廿蚊既野。<br />\n<br />\n●On a budget自然將貨就價，荷包鬆動既咪對自己好d。<br />\n每人有自己把尺，自己知道自己做緊乜，點解要咁做就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n●【去旅行去到咁辛苦有咩意思 vs 窮有窮玩無咩所謂】嗰班人唔該放過我，呢個話題仲on9過千鳥同雷切邊個勁D。<br />\n<br />\n●想笑我去旅行要訓街食垃圾你隨便，我唔撚痛既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實旅費開支最重要唔係有咩trick去慳錢，而係用錢既concept。<br />\n<br />\n好多人話「我去旅行可以好求其好慳」，咁講其實好vaguely，實際上大家個底線可以好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n可能你個Friend同你講佢好慳，你expect既係間唔時食下麵包、唔係點shopping，但冇諗過要一齊同陌生人訓dorm、坐十幾個鐘頭巴士，咁大家對「應慳得慳」就已經出現歧義。<br />\n<br />\n錢就得咁多，咁就要問返你自己其實想要d咩?<br />\n<br />\n酒店靚唔靚係咪essential?<br />\n食得好係咪essential?<br />\n<br />\n定係睇到你想睇既極光，或者熏衣草花海先係最重要?<br />\n<br />\n呢d野冇必然答案，亦唔係非黑即白不能共存；只係你要求得多自然要付出得多，一切都只係選擇黎。<br />\n<br />\n至於如果你無限錢既話，咁就講黎都冇意思了。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為你唔需要抉擇，唔需要放棄既就唔叫選擇。</span><br />\n<br />\n對我黎講，今次最重要只係睇show爬山。Most of the time我既食同住可能狗也不屌，但相對地我去晒想去既concert、爬到想爬既山，睇到想睇既風景。<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁樣答唔答到你?"},{"pid":"87e8ed1de6509314cc8a437b86cfb43cc81da66d","tid":447756,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"mont blanc係咪有條route初心者都行到<br />\n以前有個巴打話係低能級，但佢爬開山我覺得唔可以作準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d17cfa7883da9f240c23235034510eb27732109","tid":447756,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n巴打係咪有FB PAGE?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051fa66642f175fe6aaf7eab61e00e169c010123","tid":447756,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想試下呢種旅遊style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持"},{"pid":"4d927f105ae3c5f6d9eb47077d6e967112e1d4e6","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"一開始個袋有位拎左12包營多12包一丁去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/z4CMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fz4CMD.jpg&h=155c1c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港夜景真係好靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWtUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWtUV.jpg&h=7fc3a3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWHJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWHJ2.jpg&h=2ad4e291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我坐最後排左邊窗口位，但不幸地最後三排係比團大陸遊學團坐晒既，嘈都預左係基本野，精彩在後頭。 <br />\n<br />\n當我去廁所同隔離兩個死肥仔講要出去，佢地係完全冇意慾起身，係咁咦捱後少少要我係佢地膝頭前面逼出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好唔想講Mandarin所以我當佢唔醒目或者冇搭過飛機忍佢，之後有次我又想去廁所又要咁出去（即係已經第三次），到返去時佢地仍然成碌木咁坐係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我把撚火啤住佢地，一兩秒左右佢地已經察覺到，但個樣仲係傻閪閪咁望返住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為係機尾，好快已經有個空姐（好似係掃把）行過黎叫我先生麻煩坐低。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻話「我都想呀，入到先得嫁」，個空姐竟然答我「Sir，Do you want me call the police?」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根據佢地個表情我諗佢地係聽唔明句野點解，純粹見到有crew係到所以先起身比我入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就同返空姐講我諗而家ok，有咩再搵你幫手。而往後嗰幾粒鐘兩條撚樣轉死性咁靜左好多，冇再fing黎fing開，一開始係到打機仲打到抽筋咁係咁撞我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以話他媽的中国人係要管嫁！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWafD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWafD.jpg&h=9766232b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到杜拜拿拿林同班仆街講拜拜，點知去到閘口見到又係同一班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗fuck my life，好在今次唔係同佢地坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇咁鏡頭一轉已經由Gatwick去到我朋友屋企<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWJYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWJYQ.jpg&h=e508eb40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWNgT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWNgT.jpg&h=42f05e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人放左隻兔係佢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zWF1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzWF1s.jpg&h=a3dc4d59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d93d5dd99a2d840496498e357ee400d68823cd46","tid":447756,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ed59acf1946248d96bd20f6b52ba278e165040","tid":447756,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d236fd3c9913c6ed5aefd5f6207964e621035b5","tid":447756,"uid":91442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2070efd9b9ee1ace185b784f66ef629a55d279e","tid":447756,"uid":46474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"想按負皮按錯左正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82e7c82f768d99dcadd576ba2a6eca734c9cf77","tid":447756,"uid":54957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"TLDR <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔貼link 照俾正評你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b06aa27cad58b6db9184503423f75b1b20c05f2","tid":447756,"uid":117631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"1. 在雪山上有什麼心靈上的得著？<br />\n2. 什麼時候最思鄉？<br />\n3. 最多要穿幾件衣服才夠暖？"},{"pid":"5d7463866bc4e065a105b4de7a7cbc8109c56dde","tid":447756,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為去日本，我都好想可以去咁多日..."},{"pid":"df239a207eaa9df9c52edf9878b7b3b5dec0d983","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T13:53:16.000Z","msg":"係倫敦除左添gear同見朋友，值得一提就只有一個我唔夠技術留低既夕陽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zmlKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzmlKF.jpg&h=99c6d98a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBiuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBiuq.jpg&h=037028fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBOXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBOXH.jpg&h=a80f76ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我地會fast forward到兩日後既米蘭。呢程機就爽囉，坐Embraer 190 seat plan只係2x2，兩粒鐘機都有一餐得黎仲要唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最緊要係兩舊水咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBA crew普遍較老係真，但係我所見既都好撚fit，呢班一個打全機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zmHIy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzmHIy.jpg&h=ad6b1377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zmvhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzmvhG.jpg&h=de9c7653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係窗外見到阿爾卑斯山脈就知道已經到左意大利國境。我突然有種「第一次見到山」既感覺。我當然唔係第一次見到山，但嗰一刻佢就係咁樣震撼到我。<br />\n<br />\n呢種感覺我只係試過兩次。一次係坐住江之電轉入鐮倉海岸，相撲灣映入眼前一刻；以及自己下決心第一次去雪山嗰時，係JR遠望既八岳連峰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBy0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBy0x.jpg&h=af94f470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗每個90's既男仔或多或少都有點日本情義結。旅途上我不時將風景同我關於日本既記憶重疊，或者因為今次係因山而黎：而我第一次日本旅行，就係一切既原點。<br />\n<br />\n不過嗰個又係另一個故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBCoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBCoz.jpg&h=3f8b6f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總之，呢種觸電既感覺令我覺得，雖然前路茫茫，但今次過黎一定冇錯。亦係呢一刻，我決定借當時手上讀物既書名為題。"},{"pid":"270db38c6f6b8c01503c2daf98b8f6698fc64182","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mont blanc係咪有條route初心者都行到<br />\n以前有個巴打話係低能級，但佢爬開山我覺得唔可以作準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你點定義，對普通人黎講一定唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最易嗰條線對專門技術要求唔高，但好多人其實連良好體格、唔畏高、一般野外/天氣知識呢d基本要求都達唔到。"},{"pid":"16dd8ef0bb99a642be8521439800c4d6ad7b6920","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"飛Linate機場最大好處就係佢最近米蘭市中心，機場有一般巴士出市區，唔似另外兩個大機場要搭火車/專線，仲可以直情搭到去心臟地帶既Duomo。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBIzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBIzm.jpg&h=b880c09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBBOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBBOu.jpg&h=8b98946a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到city第一印象係都幾似我係書上面睇返黎的意大利。<br />\nHostel樓下，成個米蘭d樓都係呢款樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zBnUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzBnUa.jpg&h=1fe6800a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zB5Hj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzB5Hj.jpg&h=5ef744c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭兩星期我未開始戶外活動，只係做返d正常遊客野，所以係意大利係有一早book定晒住宿。呢間Hostel叫California，係唔少住宿網都應該係最平幾間之一，另一個揀佢既原因就係有kitchen。點知Check in完先發現佢封左爐頭，過兩日同d staff吹水先知係因為試過有住客搞到火燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個伏位係佢會charge城市稅同Linen，咁稅當然冇問題，但佢個Linen Charge per day其實係隱性收費用黎陰人。<br />\n<br />\n而偏偏我又有自己床單!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>係呀我有帶埋bed sheet過去，就係為左慳返呢d charge，露營時仲可以當地布訓。（歐洲有唔多但唔算少既hostel / bnb/ guestroom會收Linen Charge，而且以北歐最為流行，係北歐旅行的話有張床單其實係慳到好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</strong><br />\n<br />\n好多收Linen Charge既地方其實都係當清潔費，如果你用自己睡袋床單唔整污Joe佢d野係唔洗比的。不過佢就好堅持我一定要用佢床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲叫我千祈唔好換自己野落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我先會話佢係隱性收費陰鳩你。<br />\n<br />\n不過，即使再加返Linen Charge (per day)佢都仍然係最平之一所以我.....<br />\n<br />\nAnyway係呢到住既兩日我都叫同d staff相處得幾好，我會話佢地個人係nice，但有d怪。我又點估到，呢個係之後我連番奶野既警號...."},{"pid":"7996a1bac3f49c73405a63bb5ade62c55b5bc48c","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"其實第一日check in完已經出左Duomo行左陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過第二日夜晚要睇show所以冇行程，所以一樣早少少出市中心行陣，反正搭車都要經呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士站落車後首先見到既係Duomo背面。<br />\n真係去到後面既時候，再後面唔係好遠就係牆，好難夠位影晒全棟。不過問人借機嗰陣佢話仲有支20我就借埋，點知一拎出黎.... Lomo黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZV7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZV7z.jpg&h=23b3e317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZRqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZRqp.jpg&h=16102528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係正Duomo隔離有間好顯眼既波衫鋪，我諗都有D名氣。入面有塊display wall係名將簽名衫，當然仲有國家隊。<br />\n<br />\nBtw，現役意粉d人我好似冇個識。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZ3tP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZ3tP.jpg&h=9bd46d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZCGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZCGb.jpg&h=bdc940f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到有件祖記斜恩印晒章同字，Sale緊40歐都有少少心郁，不過XL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去過咁多歐陸教堂，米蘭大教堂外觀都係數一數二地靚，不過今日冇時間入去。旅行早段仲未摸熟部機，連相係screen / viewfinder睇同電腦睇唔同都未知，好多相以為夠光其實唔夠光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZmZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZmZF.jpg&h=cceeba19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出名既穹頂商場就係正隔離，米蘭d野其實真係集中晒係center。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZZFq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZZFq.jpg&h=833dc859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇行左幾耐就搭tram去睇show了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZe7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZe7x.jpg&h=e252dd51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6ff90879d68c10e5a1dd5d91757577c82dbb98e","tid":447756,"uid":73617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"場地叫做 Ippodromo del Galoppo di San Siro本身係馬場，不過會拎塊大草地出黎搞concert。聖西路係米蘭球場嗰區，處於West of Milan其實ok偏僻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有D野唔比入，其實都合理，佢地個做法係叫你自己影低left items完場領返。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZpR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZpR2.jpg&h=8d7c8d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果我就冇再見過我個水樽... 我老母比我嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地有兩張枱，我第一個apporach既staff (後生仔) hea望完叫我過隔離，隔離枱班妹妹非常細心咁搵過晒都冇。我再過返第一張枱，今次問第二個staff，點知一開始條友趕我走「走啦！冇呀！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n....我忍唔住捉住佢屌左兩分鐘，其他所有staff都好合作咁拉開佢即刻幫我搵。但最後都搵唔返，我覺得係因為大部份人係膠水樽，佢地見到個水壺以為係自己友d野擺埋左。我嘗試解釋呢樣野可惜佢地英文程度實在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係咁之後我行山負十幾度就冇暖水飲，屌喇星。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n今日睇既呢隊band叫 Arcade Fire。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZwZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZwZf.jpg&h=0514c96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2011年佢地攞左Grammy，贏左Eminem、全盛時期Lady Gaga、Katy Perry，仲有當年一首Need You Now街知巷聞既Lady Antebellum。<br />\n<br />\n整個網絡一片既錯鍔，「Who the fuck are Arcade Fire？」<br />\n<br />\n雖然係Indie band scene既中流砥柱，但同呢堆一線pop star比當然係冇人識；就好似聽容祖兒既人永遠多過Supper Moment。<br />\n<br />\n當年我亦只係一個冇乜己見，跟住Eminem Rap Not Afraid以為自己好型，Billboards播乜就聽乜既死靚仔。如果你同當時既我講有一日會為左佢地去意大利，我應該打死都唔信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f5npCMAok-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff5npCMAok-M&d=ZXQQO6Nfw4eyMHcwSLxa0Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=507c6e60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f5npCMAok-M</a><br />\n你睇下Dr.Dre個黑人問號樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左2017年，Arcade Fire已經係任何一個Music Festival既必然Headliner。幾乎所有音樂媒體都將2004年既debut album &quot;Funeral &quot;評為歷史最佳之一，當代樂隊地位可以話僅次Radiohed。<br />\n<br />\n到左今日，一向只涉足流行音樂既格林美，點解會比個獎風馬牛不相及既佢地仍然係不解之謎。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢D都係橫誇十幾年既後話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zFIc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzFIc3.jpg&h=4896a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/zZgKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FzZgKs.jpg&h=ad5a21fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以聽下Neighborhood #1 (Tunnels)、Crown of Love、Ready to Start呢幾首歌，不過幾乎所有樂迷都唔鐘意新碟Everything Now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2011年係美國Coachella Live亦係搖滾史上既one of the greatest moment，可惜youtube刪晒靚音質既片。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RU3-FCfIeUk?t=2m22s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRU3-FCfIeUk%3Ft%3D2m22s&d=ZXQQO6Nfw4eyMHcwSLxa0Wxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=993d8692\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RU3-FCfIeUk?t=2m22s</a>"},{"pid":"027c8ad95822b9a6ef42845f3ee4b1f0102978e3","tid":447756,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主呢"},{"pid":"77126db0af8afe536b946a3549978e00cb8c1897","tid":447756,"uid":1881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:15:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}